      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Quoting from the release notes you linked regarding <code>*</code>: <b>this is not secure and not recommended</b>; so you need additional measures to secure the connection, such as SSH (?), see also &quot;<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/q/33184800\">Is it safe to expose java remote debugger port to the internet?</a>&quot;"
